# Detection
 
## Event ID 4768 — Kerberos authentication ticket (TGT) was requested
 
If PKINIT authentication is not common in the environment, an Event ID 4768 where the **Certificate Information** attributes are populated (Certificate Issuer Name, Certificate Serial Number, Certificate Thumbprint) can indicate anomalous behavior — particularly when originating from a host that has no business performing certificate-based authentication.

